                </p>
                <p>
                    Clear Window provides a platform for verified, anonymous reviews. Our unique approach allows you to share honest feedback while maintaining your anonymity—we verify your connection to the property or service you're reviewing, then immediately anonymize your identity.
                </p>

                <div class="info-box">
